醫院搶救，可惜最終搶救不治，警方正調查意外原因。"},{"pid":"6b5b779757fcf29ad698ff8d33f45cb6f904af31","tid":996443,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"屌d撚樣都唔知點渣車既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baacf36bbacd3abf91a2534c487f1a05710f44f3","tid":996443,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b5b779757fcf29ad698ff8d33f45cb6f904af31","tid":996443,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"屌d撚樣都唔知點渣車既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"貨車撞吊臂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}